{"type": "article", "id": 32337, "title": "运动品牌里买UA的人最有钱，以及，推荐Mansur Gavriel格纹包 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-19T02:48:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12311, "name": "水桶包"}, {"id": 32889, "name": "数字参与度"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 2684, "name": "Mansur Gavriel"}, {"id": 5438, "name": "Dolce & Gabbana"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 28551, "name": "Champion"}, {"id": 32890, "name": "Evine Live"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160919101455Rv9hL8AM1YaqbgXK.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2016/business/athletic-outdoor/report-under-armour-nike-shoppers-income-257960/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Under Armour 的消费者年收入可能更高</b></a> | 来自纽约的调研机构 You Gov 调研了 20 万名消费者，它指出，运动品牌消费者中，Under Armour 的消费者年收入超过 5 万美元的比例更大。其中，有 53% 的 Under Armour 消费者年收入超过 5 万美元。排名第二的品牌是 Asics，年收入超 5 万美元的消费者比例为 52.7%，接下来分别是 Vans，New Balance，Adidas。排名最后的是 Nike 和 Converse，分别为 32% 和 30%。 You Gov 的分析师称，因为 Nike 和 Converse 极高的曝光率，它的消费者来自更为广泛的收入群体。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/dolce-gabbanas-local-retail-revolution\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Dolce &amp; Gabbana 将进行门店本地化翻新计划</b></a> | 据 Domenico Dolce 称，Dolce &amp; Gabbana 将在全球范围内进行门店本地化翻新计划，这个计划旨在废弃品牌统一的门店装修风格，为 Dolce &amp; Gabbana 的门店加入更多的具有辨识度的本地元素，让不同地区的消费者拥有不同的购物体验。该计划将于 9 月 24 日米兰时装周期间，在米兰首次进行。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/media-features/michael-kors-victoria-beckham-lead-in-digital-engagement-ratings-10550735/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>纽约时装周期间，数字参与度最高的品牌是 Michael Kors </b></a>| 在 9 月 7 日至 9 月 15 日的纽约时装周期间， 根据各大时尚品牌的网络搜索量及点赞数等数据生成了一份 ListenFirst Digital Engagement 排行榜。该榜单显示，Michael Kors 的数字参与度最高，共计 960 万次。排名第二的是 Victoria Beckham，提及数共计 430 万次。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/tommy-hilfiger-morris-goldfarb-mottola-invest-evine-live-10547450/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tommy Hilfiger 等多位投资人联手投资 Evine Live</b></a> |  Evine Live 是美国跨平台视频电商公司，销售的产品包括珠宝、手表、家居、美妆、健身及电子产品。此次投资包括 Tommy Hilfiger、Morris Goldfarb、Tommy Mottola 等多位知名的投资人，Evine 将以每股 1.68 美元的价格，向他们出售 1000 万美元的普通股。不过，此次投资纯属个人投资，与投资者的公司并无关系。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>今年秋季，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/y-3-super-zip-closer-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3 带来了全新的 Super Zip 鞋款</a>。以 adidas Originals 经典的 Superstar 为原型，鞋舌上的可以拆卸的拉链皮革成为了该鞋款的设计亮点。这双鞋的售价为 340 美元，现在已于 <a href=\"http://store.y-3.com/us/y3store/sneakers_cod11057130uk.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Y-3 官网</a>发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100658ar1WnCultKFh0jMN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100658faHSWPMdLoxp6VT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100700OlqJGh0NyQCKdt9R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100709BN0RQDuVCnMIjyri.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016091910071072Q9srdlBOuZHFIw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100719Wxwg0uGYZ4DIe8HC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>凭借着水桶包的大热，成为时尚界传奇的 Mansur Gavriel ，发布了 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/the-new-mansur-accessoriess/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017 春季新品</a>预览。该系列新品延续了品牌一贯的简约风格，用上等的皮革打造。此外，色彩变得更丰富了，还加入了新鲜的格纹元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100729bUGajhtL4rZl9KOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100729ytnQSoalgFM8mH4q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100729NdyD0LtPA4bzqTo7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100730NMKZuEYC3q5z9g04.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100730Dxi3q7FXY4GQE9hr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100729RHcO8twFg1Vfx7aj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100738KBp9fAi6geqbjN3l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100737UaqYZb2pyGkA9x81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100737pIsRTWF5z3Af8ndB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609191007458VMoBvSZNXkqsadC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100745cwaVuNyUl532Qbr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本时尚品牌 nonnative 与 Converse 正式发布全新联名 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/nonnative-x-converse-pro-leather\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pro Leather 系列</a>，以庆祝 Pro Leather 的 40 岁生日。这双鞋共有棕、白、黑三种颜色，鞋身以粗糙质感的麂皮代替了皮革，并在鞋舌处加入金属拉链，展现复古情怀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100756ONXvmDqgwp2Ssk9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609191007562E9GxtscaDiQZPJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100926cHZjuponfhPbez0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">美国街头品牌 Champion 邀请了日本著名造型师伊藤信子为它拍摄 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/champion-2016-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">2016 秋冬 Lookbook。&nbsp;</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100941PxRrjBUmGAWaOd6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100942TRbIM8XOSd14fhC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100955DFo4VWcl8rnkqjAC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919100955ylikSOzeMYxwWv9A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Topshop 也开始了它的第一个“即看即买”系列。它发布的 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/topshop-spring-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017 春季新作</a>以 1980 年代的复古风为主题，现已经可以通过官网进行购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609191010287rmgfhlN3AdLSGYs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919101028hpTu7zItcQBqfxgo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919101041lLTfaXFmC3UKpgWO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919101141BLHmOVwTzoDhlWxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.508876\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919101141fhBgcCJYMwaKUzqn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919101141ceZAKdsoI5G1j4rl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.507143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}